videos.description: CSU Bakersfield pass the ball around and Justin Pride finishes with the scoop layup.
videos.headline: CSU Bakersfield's Pride with the nice scoop layup

videos.description: CSU Bakersfield's Dedrick Basile finds the cutting Moataz Aly who finishes with the slam dunk.
videos.headline: CSU Bakersfield's Aly finishes with the power jam

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Tadric Jackson brings the ball up the court and makes a 3-pointer at the buzzer to end the first half.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Jackson drains 3-pointer as the buzzer

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Josh Pastner explains talks about the miss opportunities of his team in the 1st half.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's coach Josh Pastner talks about how his team can improve in the 2nd half

videos.description: Corey Heyward finds Josh Okogie who finishes with the finger roll for Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Okogie with the nice finger roll lay-up

videos.description: Tadric Jackson finds Josh Okogie all alone and he finishes with the big dunk for Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Okogie attacks the rim and finishes with the dunk
